  "active_lock_reason": "resolved",
  "body": "If a user logs a number using \"%d\" in `console.log` they will see an incorrect result. This is because EVM numbers are represented using BN.js, and casting those to `number` looses precision.\r\n\r\nWe should somehow detect this case and turn those numbers into strings.",
